{"tid":1992530,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發］2020 DSE數學卷一因疫情緣故流出（多圖）","createTime":"2020-04-28T07:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T08:25:01.000Z","uid":357251,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"09f62ec2246466df905a34436f99b2c7ee804304","tid":1992530,"uid":357251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:59:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好信標題黨</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n今年DSER 上半年因為社運，有啲每次出嚟都要冒着生命危險同埋用前途做賭注，有啲為咗出嚟同屋企人反面，佢哋已經好攰，仲有啲依家俾人告緊，可能已經冇咗考嘅機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下半年因為武漢肺炎，冇咗last day，冇得考mock，冇得補習，仲要延期，可能佢哋plan咗好耐嘅strategy已經用唔番，依家又要冒着生命危險去考，如果瀨咗嘢一係0分，一係扣分，佢哋辛苦咁耐咪白費咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我道歉呃咗你地入嚟，但係見到熱門post冇乜俾應屆考生鼓勵，想連登仔多啲關懷下佢哋，我覺得呢個時候應該重拾你哋嘅人性，等佢哋捱過呢一個難關</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後想講一句<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人唔會放棄你哋，應屆考生唔該俾啲掙扎，同埋想話比你哋聽，有人會支持你地㗎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81e124aca02ce5f34736944d04002a4ebbf6f3f","tid":1992530,"uid":357251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:59:44.000Z","m